title: Rent a home, not a dorm!
posting_body: ['Our Community is A+', 'REMARKABLE AMENITIES, APARTMENTS AND LOCATION!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Ironwood at the Ranch', '11705 Decatur Street, Westminster, CO, 80234', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 737 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Ironwood Apartments at The Ranch features modern and impressive one and two-bedroom apartments for rent in Westminster, CO with contemporary features including stainless-steel appliances, full-size washer and dryers, custom cabinets, large closets, fireplaces, bright windows, wood flooring and plush cut Berber carpeting and vaulted ceilings in third-floor homes.', 'This is the way living was meant to be.', 'Welcome to the good life.', 'Welcome to Ironwood.', 'Call or stop in today to reserve your new apartment!', 'Features', '- Private Patio or Balcony', '- Oversized Windows with 2?', 'Cottage Blinds', '- Stainless Steel Energy Star® Appliances', '- Extended-Room Shower Rods', '- Designer Pendant Lighting', '- Large Closets with Organizers', '- Designer Lighting and Two-Toned Paint', '- Rain Shower Heads', '- Cherry Wood or White Custom Wood Cabinets', '- Full-Size Washer and Dryer', '- Roman Soaking Tubs', '- Wood-Style Plank Flooring', '- Modern Single-Handle Pullout Kitchen Faucets', '*Note: Some features may not be available in all apartment homes.', 'Floor plans and dimensions are approximate.', 'Community Amenities', '- WiFi Throughout the Common Areas', '- Pet-friendly Community with Dog Park', '- Barbeque Grills and Seating Areas', '- Resort-Style Pool and Spa', '- A Grand Café with Complimentary Coffee', '- The Ranch Golf Course Community', '- Resident Lounge', '- Business Center with Computers and Printer', '- State-of-the-Art Fitness Center', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Bd4kZsP7']
